    Class Description

    CheckConnectivityCommand
    Check if we have basic connection to the DB.

    A query that creates the Atlas DB schema with all the tables.

    Get all categories from the DB.
    GetGeoLocationsQuery
    Get all locations name and ID's from the DB

    SearchResultsQuery

    UpdateFavoritesQuery

    UpdatePersonQuery
    Query for updating and editing an existing person from the DB.
